No, it is imagined, it is imagined.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Çûk sêwir na?
 
The bird is an imagination, isn't it?

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Ooo, çûk sêwir e.
 
Ooo, the bird is an imagination.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:21,000
